channel.title: Comments on: Melody Ehsani Wax Print Nail Wraps

item.title: By: Sarah Cosper
item.dc:creator: Sarah Cosper
item.description:
In reply to <a href="/melody-ehsani-wax-print-nail-wraps/#comment-117">Trina</a>.
You can use them on your toes. You could probably use them on your fingers too. They'll work on short nails!
